## 🐛 Bug Report

When attempting to merge cells that have been duplicated using the "duplicateRow" method, an error is consistently arising: "Cannot merge already merged cells." This persists despite using the "unMergeCells" method and confirming the "isMerged" status as "false" for these cells.

Lib version: 4.3.0 & 4.4.0

## Steps To Reproduce

While iterating through a user list and duplicating rows to add x number of users, a recurring issue surfaces. Previously, resolving this issue involved using the "unmergeCells" method, yet this time, it persists despite employing this previously successful solution.

```javascript
let isFirstStakeholderInsert = true;
criticalRiskActivity.criticalRiskActivitiesStakeholder.forEach(
  (cras, num) => {
    if (!isFirstStakeholderInsert) {
      copySheet.duplicateRow(24 + extraRows, 1, true);
      extraRows += 1;

      copySheet.unMergeCells(`D${24 + extraRows}:F${24 + extraRows}`);
      copySheet.unMergeCells(`D${24 + extraRows}`);
      copySheet.unMergeCells(`E${24 + extraRows}`);
      copySheet.unMergeCells(`F${24 + extraRows}`);
      copySheet.getCell(`D${24 + extraRows}`).unmerge();
      copySheet.getCell(`E${24 + extraRows}`).unmerge();
      copySheet.getCell(`F${24 + extraRows}`).unmerge();

      console.log(`D${24 + extraRows}`, copySheet.getCell(`D${24 + extraRows}`).isMerged);
      console.log(`E${24 + extraRows}`, copySheet.getCell(`E${24 + extraRows}`).isMerged);
      console.log(`F${24 + extraRows}`, copySheet.getCell(`F${24 + extraRows}`).isMerged);

      copySheet.mergeCells(`D${24 + extraRows}:F${24 + extraRows}`);
    }

    copySheet.getCell(`B${24 + extraRows}`).value = `${num + 1}`;
    copySheet.getCell(`C${24 + extraRows}`).value = `${
      cras.stakeholder.maternalLastname
        ? cras.stakeholder.parentalLastname +
          ' ' +
          cras.stakeholder.maternalLastname +
          ', ' +
          cras.stakeholder.name
        : cras.stakeholder.parentalLastname +
          ', ' +
          cras.stakeholder.name
    }`;
    isFirstStakeholderInsert = false;
  }
);
```

